quran[19]{c,v,t}:
  87,1,"Glorify the name of your Lord, the Most High"
  87,2,Who created and fashioned in due proportion
  87,3,"and Who determined [the creation] then guided them"
  87,4,and Who brings forth the pasture
  87,5,then makes it into withered chaff
  87,6,"We will teach you [the Qur’an], so you will not forget"
  87,7,"except what Allah wills, for indeed He knows what is manifest and what is hidden"
  87,8,We will guide you to the easy way
  87,9,"So remind, if the reminder should benefit"
  87,10,He who fears Allah will take heed
  87,11,but the wretched will avoid it
  87,12,who will enter the Great Fire
  87,13,wherein he will neither die nor live
  87,14,"Indeed, he who purifies himself will attain success"
  87,15,and remembers his Lord’s Name and prays
  87,16,But you prefer the life of this world
  87,17,even though the Hereafter is better and more lasting
  87,18,"Indeed, this was in the earlier Scriptures"
  87,19,the Scriptures of Abraham and Moses